description:
This course explores an aspect of drama before 1660 intensively; specific course topics will vary from year to year. 

See the English Department's website at www.english.upenn.edu for a description of the current offerings.
name: TOPICS DRAMA TO 1660: Greatsouled/Graceful:  Classical & Christian Ethics in Plays of Shakespeare
